Release Manager Doc
===================

This document is a checklist of all the actiities to be
done for a release.

* Verify backword compatibility: ./testBackwardCompatibility.sh

* Update/add all the site docs: src/site

* Update the MAN page: src/main/doc/wizcrypt.man

* Change version info in:
  => pom.xml
  => src/main/resources/org/wiztools/wizcrypt/VERSION
  => src/main/shell/wizcrypt
  => wizcrypt.spec

* Create a sibversion tag with the version number

* Upload the artifacts to release site

* Update site with: target/site

* Update http://freshmeat.net/

* Update new POM and Jars in Maven public repository

* Blog, digg, etc!

